## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="3040c-122">發音 lexicon 是字詞或片語，以及使用適當的發音字母指定及其發聲的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3040c-122">A pronunciation lexicon is a collection of words or phrases together with their pronunciations specified using an appropriate pronunciation alphabet.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3040c-123">這個方法通常稱為平台基礎結構，以回應<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis>架構的應用程式呼叫<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A>並使用目前所實作的合成語音<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml>執行個體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3040c-123">This method is typically called by the platform infrastructure in response to a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis> based applications calling <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> and using the synthesizer voice implemented by the current <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml> instance.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="3040c-124">值`mediaType`通常是 MIME 規格，因為 SSML 規格使用 MIME 媒體規格。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3040c-124">The value of `mediaType` is typically a MIME specification, as the SSML specification uses MIME for media specifications.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="3040c-125">實作<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A>使用<xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite>介面傳遞至從資源載入詞典 」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3040c-125">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.AddLexicon%2A> uses the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.ITtsEngineSite> interface passed in to load a lexicon from a resource.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="3040c-126">然後將儲存`System.IO.Stream`到詞典 」 中`System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary`執行個體，以詞典 URI 編製索引。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="3040c-126">It then stores a `System.IO.Stream` to the lexicon in a `System.Collections.Generic.Dictionary` instance, indexed by the lexicon URI.</span></span>  
  
```  
public static Dictionary<Uri, Stream> _aLexicons = new Dictionary<Uri, Stream>();  
  
 public void AddLexicon(Uri uri, string mediaType, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
    Stream stream = site.LoadResource(uri, mediaType);  
    _aLexicons.Add(uri, stream);  
}  
  
 public void RemoveLexicon(Uri uri, ITtsEngineSite site) {  
     Stream stream;  
     if (_aLexicons.TryGetValue(uri, out stream)) {  
         stream.Close();  
         _aLexicons.Remove(uri);  
     }  
}  
  
```

  
  
